					<msContents>
						<summary>

						<p>States that <hi rend="bold">Mōṭṭupalli Golla-Manda</hi> gave 25 cows for a perpetual lamp in the temple of Prasanna Chennakēśava of <hi rend="bold">Mōṭṭupalli</hi> and that a piece of land was given to the cowherd who was to feed those cows and supply ghee for the lamp.</p>						

						</summary>
